20.11	Henry_Hill_(mobster)	Henry Hill	Henry Hill (born June 11, 1943) is a former American mobster. A Lucchese crime family associate, Hill became an FBI informant whose life story was documented in the book Wiseguy, written by crime reporter, Nicholas Pileggi. The 1990 Martin Scorsese film, Goodfellas, was based on the book, with Hill played by Ray Liotta.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/47/Henryhillmugshot.jpg/220px-Henryhillmugshot.jpg
